# --- vendored Bongos action bar engine (standalone; dormant while the standalone
# Bongos addon is enabled -- see bongos\gate.lua). Order mirrors Bongos.toc:
# gate first, then libs -> core -> actionbar subsystem. The Garnet right-click menu
# (bongos\menu.lua) and the Actionbars settings tab replace Bongos's own options UI;
# its menu.xml / options/ / slash.lua were intentionally dropped (not vendored).
