# --- vendored pfUI skin engine (standalone; dormant while pfUI is enabled) ---
# A near-verbatim copy of pfUI's skin subsystem, renamed pfUI -> pfSkin. See
# pfskin\boot.lua. Order matters: boot first (creates the namespace + gate),
# api before ui-widgets (api resets pfSkin.api), config before login. Skins only
# register, so their order is free. TBC-only skins self-skip via the version gate.
pfskin\boot.lua
pfskin\compat.lua
pfskin\api.lua
pfskin\ui-widgets.lua
pfskin\config.lua
# nameplates module + its libs (ported from pfUI; gated by the PfUI-nameplates toggle).
# locale data (spell cast times / debuff durations) MUST load before libcast (reads L at load).
# Order mirrors pfUI's init/libs.xml: tipscan -> spell -> cast -> debuff -> throttle, then the module.
